ates_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the race developed, the USA (6:32.48) overhauled long-time leaders China (6:33.60), and Denmark (6:35.65) also rowed past the Irish boat who had to settle for fourth, in 6:38.10.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.7774329075085131, \"rank\": 0.267714037204189, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9826081395130656, \"rank\": 0.015257938615348054, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.989097028170628, \"rank\": 0.009728416600380095, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9695785990972475, \"rank\": 0.0211213845715724, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the B final Ireland will take on Denmark and Australia and will look to finish their Games on a high note.\", \"f